<br>
Also, good and evil are separately working on big alliances so that they are able to fight bigger mobs.  There is some thread in the RP forum for an alliance of 5-6 evil guilds and the some good guilds are working on an alliance of 6-8 guilds which isn't discussed here.  <br>
<br>
As the server is small, we'll only have a few guilds ever able to kill the bigger mobs by themselves, some guilds will band together to do it, and most guilds will never abide to anything as they will be small and stay small but they will still have as much fun as everyone else.<br>
<br>
Do we need a rotation?  No, because if you ask me, we don't have enough people to go and kill the 'uber' mobs in the first place.  It might totally s*ck that the server has a small population, but at least it does fix certain issues. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#A62A2A>- </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4>The Soapbox</a> <font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href="http://www.firiona-vie.com/">Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.firiona-vie.com/fvchat.html" target="_blank"><h3>Chat Room</a></h3></center> <br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.5<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  